::: With a small rumble, the cruiser sailed throguh the Transwarp corridor 
and into the orbit of Prehistoric earth. The vessle was a small battle class 
ship with basic wepons and systems. :::

::: A Predacon stood on the bridge, seated across from his partner and 
associate. He gazed out towrds the planet and then back to his scanners. They 
had finally found what they were looking for. ::::

::: Set ::: Shuko, I think weve finally got them. The price we paid for there 
location was well worth it. And with all this stable energon we can both 
boast our fortunes!

::: Set agian looked outward. He was a Predacon business man with one love in 
life. Money. The more he had the happier he was. He invested alot in this 
projected and expected results. He then turned his silver and black plated 
face towrds Shuko :::

::: Set ::: Soon we will have the Oblitercons agian, and with them no one 
will defy us agian!
